| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5630 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a764726a-71a2-5b4e-9086-4342587cb14d"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
